      <title>ETF 高管变动带来积极影响：VettaFi 的 Rosenbluth</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/etf-executive-changes-a-positive-vettafi-s-rosenbluth-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[VettaFi 研究主管 Todd Rosenbluth 比较了先锋集团和贝莱德的发行人流动情况，并预计高盛将成为未来一年值得关注的 ETF 参与者。他对最近的高管变动持乐观态度，并讨论了他对这些公司发展的预期。Todd Rosenbluth 在“彭博 ETF IQ”节目中与 Katie Greifeld、Scarlet Fu 和 Eric Balchunas 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/etf-executive-changes-a-positive-vettafi-s-rosenbluth-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:51:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行将在法国逐步增加员工：Vanessa Holtz</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/bofa-to-add-staff-incrementally-in-france-vanessa-holtz-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行计划逐步在法国增加员工，在英国脱欧后将数百名员工转移到巴黎，因此扩张速度有所放缓。这是美国银行证券欧洲负责人兼法国地区执行官凡妮莎·霍尔茨 (Vanessa Holtz) 的说法。霍尔茨在巴黎彭博社的新声音活动上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/bofa-to-add-staff-incrementally-in-france-vanessa-holtz-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:50:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Skydance 以每股 23 美元的价格收购派拉蒙有表决权的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/skydance-is-said-to-offer-23-a-share-for-paramount-voting-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Skydance Media 计划向派拉蒙全球有投票权股票的投资者提供每股 23 美元的价格，这是与这家影视巨头合并计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/skydance-is-said-to-offer-23-a-share-for-paramount-voting-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 16:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将出售 25 亿欧元德国电信股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/deutsche-telekom-investor-kfw-to-sell-2-5-billion-in-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国正在出售其所持有的德国电信股份公司 (Deutsche Telekom AG) 价值 25 亿欧元（合 27 亿美元）的股份，这是德国政府为剥离部分公司资产而采取的一系列举措中的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/deutsche-telekom-investor-kfw-to-sell-2-5-billion-in-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 16:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着新的指控浮出水面，道明银行贿赂丑闻蔓延至佛罗里达州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/td-s-bribery-woes-spread-to-florida-as-fresh-allegations-surface</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行佛罗里达州分行一名长期工作人员收受了数笔 200 美元的贿赂，以帮助客户绕过反洗钱法规将数百万美元转移到哥伦比亚，这一指控进一步加剧了该银行在美国面临的法律问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/td-s-bribery-woes-spread-to-florida-as-fresh-allegations-surface</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:33:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制造业疲软导致股市下跌、债券上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-as-rate-cut-bets-firm-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的制造业报告引发了人们对世界最大经济体进一步失去动力的担忧，华尔街交易员推低了股票价格，推高了债券价格。油价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-as-rate-cut-bets-firm-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油输出国组织意外增产计划加剧市场悲观情绪，导致油价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油输出国组织 (OPEC+) 意外推出今年恢复部分市场生产的计划后，油价暴跌，进一步加剧了原油几个月来一直呈现的看跌势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 22:10:44 GMT</pubDate>
